  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Documentation of cases of sexual violence including the victims current situation.\r\n    Focus group discussions\r\n    Training of district stakeholders\r\n     Conducting reproductive health camps\r\n     Trainings of local health providers.\r\n     Workshops on issues relating to reproductive health and rights\r\n     Psycho-social counseling sessions in connection to the medical camps. Training of community psycho-social workers \r\n    Workshops on general awareness relating psycho-social issues\r\n    Information submitted to the TRC and other relevant transitional justice mechanisms.\r\n    Interactions with Commissioners concerning the findings of the report\r\n    Legal counseling to victims referred by medical camps \r\n    Training for stakeholders such as police, CDOs, PLC’s, local lawyers"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
